8 void DWAPlanner::load_params(void)
9 {
10  // - A -
11  local_nh_.param<double>("ANGLE_RESOLUTION", angle_resolution_, 0.087);
12  local_nh_.param<double>("ANGLE_TO_GOAL_TH", angle_to_goal_th_, M_PI);
13  // - F -
14  local_nh_.param<double>("FOOTPRINT_PADDING", footprint_padding_, 0.01);
15  // - G -
16  local_nh_.param<std::string>("GLOBAL_FRAME", global_frame_, std::string("map"));
17  local_nh_.param<double>("GOAL_THRESHOLD", dist_to_goal_th_, 0.1);
18  // - H -
19  local_nh_.param<double>("HZ", hz_, 20);
20  // - M -
21  local_nh_.param<double>("MAX_ACCELERATION", max_acceleration_, 0.5);
22  local_nh_.param<double>("MAX_DECELERATION", max_deceleration_, 2.0);
23  local_nh_.param<double>("MAX_D_YAWRATE", max_d_yawrate_, 3.2);
24  local_nh_.param<double>("MAX_IN_PLACE_YAWRATE", max_in_place_yawrate_, 0.6);
25  local_nh_.param<double>("MAX_VELOCITY", max_velocity_, 1.0);
26  local_nh_.param<double>("MAX_YAWRATE", max_yawrate_, 1.0);
27  local_nh_.param<double>("MIN_IN_PLACE_YAWRATE", min_in_place_yawrate_, 0.3);
28  local_nh_.param<double>("MIN_VELOCITY", min_velocity_, 0.0);
29  local_nh_.param<double>("MIN_YAWRATE", min_yawrate_, 0.05);
30  // - O -
31  local_nh_.param<double>("OBSTACLE_COST_GAIN", obs_cost_gain_, 1.0);
32  local_nh_.param<double>("OBS_RANGE", obs_range_, 2.5);
33  // - P -
34  local_nh_.param<double>("PATH_COST_GAIN", path_cost_gain_, 0.4);
35  local_nh_.param<double>("PREDICT_TIME", predict_time_, 3.0);
36  // - R -
37  local_nh_.param<std::string>("ROBOT_FRAME", robot_frame_, std::string("base_link"));
38  local_nh_.param<double>("ROBOT_RADIUS", robot_radius_, 0.1);
39  // - S -
40  local_nh_.param<double>("SIM_DIRECTION", sim_direction_, M_PI / 2.0);
41  local_nh_.param<double>("SIM_PERIOD", sim_period_, 0.1);
42  local_nh_.param<int>("SIM_TIME_SAMPLES", sim_time_samples_, 10);
43  local_nh_.param<double>("SLEEP_TIME_AFTER_FINISH", sleep_time_after_finish_, 0.5);
44  local_nh_.param<double>("SLOW_VELOCITY_TH", slow_velocity_th_, 0.1);
45  local_nh_.param<double>("SPEED_COST_GAIN", speed_cost_gain_, 0.4);
46  local_nh_.param<int>("SUBSCRIBE_COUNT_TH", subscribe_count_th_, 3);
47  // - T -
48  local_nh_.param<double>("TARGET_VELOCITY", target_velocity_, 0.55);
49  local_nh_.param<double>("TO_GOAL_COST_GAIN", to_goal_cost_gain_, 0.8);
50  local_nh_.param<double>("TURN_DIRECTION_THRESHOLD", turn_direction_th_, 0.1);
51  // - U -
52  local_nh_.param<bool>("USE_FOOTPRINT", use_footprint_, false);
53  local_nh_.param<bool>("USE_PATH_COST", use_path_cost_, false);
54  local_nh_.param<bool>("USE_SCAN_AS_INPUT", use_scan_as_input_, false);
55  // - V -
56  local_nh_.param<int>("VELOCITY_SAMPLES", velocity_samples_, 3);
57  local_nh_.param<double>("V_PATH_WIDTH", v_path_width_, 0.05);
58  // - Y -
59  local_nh_.param<int>("YAWRATE_SAMPLES", yawrate_samples_, 20);
60 
61  target_velocity_ = std::min(target_velocity_, max_velocity_);
62 }
